const theme = createTheme();

export default function ManagerWorkspace() {

    const [pass, setPassword] = useState("");
    const [employees, setEmployees] = useState([{ Name: "aaa" }, { Name: "bbb" }, { Name: "ccc" }]);

    const activateAlgorithm = (event) => {
        event.preventDefault();
        axios.get(`https://localhost:44382/api/Mamager/${pass}`)
            .then(res => {
                console.log(res.data);
            }).catch(err => console.log(err))
    };

    return (
        <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
            <Container component="main" maxWidth="xs">
                <CssBaseline />
                <Box>
                    <List
                        sx={{ width: '100%', maxWidth: 360, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}
                        aria-label="contacts"
                    >
                        {employees.map((item, index) => (
                            <ListItem disablePadding>
                                <ListItemButton>
                                    <ListItemIcon>
                                        <BoyIcon />
                                    </ListItemIcon>
                                    <ListItemText primary={item.Name} />
                                </ListItemButton>
                            </ListItem>
                        ))}
                    </List>

                    <TextField
                        margin="normal"
                        required
                        fullWidth
                        name="start"
                        label="החל מ"
                        type="number"
                        id="start"
                        autoComplete="current-start"
                    />
                    <TextField
                        margin="normal"
                        required
                        fullWidth
                        name="end"
                        label="עד ל"
                        type="number"
                        id="end"
                        autoComplete="current-end"
                    /> <Button
                        type="button"
                        fullWidth
                        variant="contained"
                        sx={{ mt: 3, mb: 2 }}
                        onClick={activateAlgorithm}
                    >
                        הפעלת האלגוריתם
                    </Button>
                </Box>
            </Container >
        </ThemeProvider >
    )
}
